{"tid":1724185,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府突然抽起理大位於何文田的斜坡校園擴建14億撥款","createTime":"2019-11-15T11:43:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T11:59:43.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a86c3e1138456570189174890e4704b8906f0f8b","tid":1724185,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:43:00.000Z","msg":"食物及衞生局副局長徐德義今午(15日)在立法會財務委員會會議上提出，決定臨時抽起理工大學位於何文田的斜坡校園擴建工程，涉逾14億港元的撥款，稱因不同人士對項目有不同意見，當局希望有更多時間諮詢。多名泛民議員反對有關做法，議員區諾軒指現時貿然抽起項目，質疑當局想優先審議公務員加薪。議員邵家臻問政府是否想放棄年輕人，放棄大學。<br />\n<br />\n建制派議員何俊賢表示，吐露港公路被中大學生堵塞，反映大學機制有問題，對撥款予大學有保留。另一議員梁志祥認同暫時收回有關項目，待問題解決後再繼續商討。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191115/bkn-20191115171444817-1115_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191115%2Fbkn-20191115171444817-1115_00822_001.html&d=NKgE6Majit0rEYuBm%2F0CvkZZ0ArqIWVBMBEeODt8eII%3D&h=bdb413d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191115/bkn-20191115171444817-1115_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4fc4e25a5d123f1627062d57f50941cc9531eeed","tid":1724185,"uid":220766,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:46:56.000Z","msg":"陣間俾+x搶左去捐筆錢唔好喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8997c9f2104a53b13733f99d3a9f1d51fdf8e84d","tid":1724185,"uid":71935,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:48:09.000Z","msg":"要奉獻俾偉大既祖國"},{"pid":"3f21a2c8dc62fe06290cbba3082ec94516981870","tid":1724185,"uid":301050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:48:42.000Z","msg":"你咁樣我係唔會驚架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff7309447a1410b067a3f0e7cefcf9b606ecfcc4","tid":1724185,"uid":303677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:52:36.000Z","msg":"起唔起都唔關poly手足事架啦 都畢哂業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"968fa942672f23a2e9def28557cd485